description._content: Description: The Fields Manager's bungalow at M.-i-S. with Mr. J.L. Wright, Fields Manager, and his assistant,Mr. M.C. Seamark, 1926. Date: 1926 Description: The new chemical laboratory at the Oil-Fields-under construction, 1926. Date: 1926 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/714 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
